# Scientific-Calculator
A scientific calculator is a type of electronic calculator, generally, but not always handheld, designed to calculate problems in science, engineering and mathematics. They have almost completely replaced slide rules in almost all traditional applications, and are widely used in education and industry.
The Calculator application performs both basic and scientific operations" The application providesuser an option to choose between the basic mode and scientific mode based on the optionselected by the user, the application calls the corresponding class and the user can performvarious mathematical operations provided in the class. There is a base class in the applicationwhich contains all the methods for calculation, basic as well as scientific. The applicationvalidates the user input also and provides appropriate messages when wrong input is given by the user                               
